{"tid":133730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華今早將交提名表","createTime":"2017-02-25T01:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T03:28:41.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97dbce850c6e392e330abcf0dbd13c16f75674de","tid":133730,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:01:25.000Z","msg":"曾俊華今早將交提名表<br />\n2017-02-25 HKT 08:47<br />\n<br />\n行政長官參選人曾俊華，將於今早率先到選舉事務處遞交提名表。<br />\n<br />\n他的競選辦公室今早發出採訪通知，曾俊華將於早上10時半，到位於灣仔的選舉事務處交表。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官選舉提名期將於下星期三結束。"},{"pid":"75d8d7c4e94b41369fb9409059b4f3c3307977a4","tid":133730,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6393ec4a12a98c9ae570476767283a88a5366ff9","tid":133730,"uid":10442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:20:08.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛確認書？"},{"pid":"0a06c5e92bb3f4d9f1b845d8cf182c138889f600","tid":133730,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:20:26.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dbb51f909cb7b3e580ce9b2a93d076d45dd474","tid":133730,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim